@prefix ex: <http://example.org/> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

# subClassOf 传递
ex:Scientist rdfs:subClassOf ex:Agent .
# 类型继承（每个实例继承两层）
ex:newton a ex:Person .
ex:newton a ex:Agent .
ex:curie a ex:Person .
ex:curie a ex:Agent .
